com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.listener
Interface AttachCopyCallback

public interface AttachCopyCallback

Instances of user defined native classes implementing this interface are notified when attaching a non-native (detached) copy.

Author:
Jose M. Arranz Santamaria
See Also:
